\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 While the global AI race is often framed as a competition between nations, a more insidious transformation is unfolding within nations themselves\'97especially those leading in AI development. Closed, proprietary AI systems are poised to 
\f0\b concentrate wealth and control in ways that make past industrial revolutions look egalitarian by comparison
\f1\b0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

